                                                                                                                                     
Pirate Faction Review                                                                                                              
                                                                                                                                     
  The four pirate factions are the central antagonist set in Ace Trader. Each owns one quadrant of the galaxy, has a distinct combat
  identity hard-coded in stat modifiers, and creates a clear difficulty curve as the player explores outward.                           
